==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Monopolize
<hw>Mo*nop"o*lize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Monopolized</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Monopolizing</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>.]</vmorph> <ety>[From
<er>Monopoly</er>.]</ety> <def>To acquire a monopoly of; to have or get
the exclusive privilege or means of dealing in, or the exclusive
possession of; to engross the whole of; <as>as, to <ex>monopolize</ex>
the coffee trade; to <ex>monopolize</ex> land.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monopolizer</ent>⟦br⟧
